    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Clan</p><p>Prerequisite: Fūshin Clan</p><p>The wind itself has adopted you as one of its own. You gain the following benefits</p><p>• Increase your Intelligence or Dexterity score by 1, to a maximum of 20</p><p>• You can use Dexterity instead of Intelligence as your casting modifier for Fūshin Clan Hijutsu</p><p>• You ignore difficult terrain and visual obstructions created by wind or jutsu with the Wind Release Keyword.</p><p>• You gain a +1d8 bonus to clash checks when clashing with a jutsu with the Wind Release keyword</p>",
